    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing this letter to express my deep concern over my missing credit card. I received a package from your bank yesterday, and I was requested to acknowledge the receipt of a credit card along with the package. However, to my surprise, as I opened the package the card was not present there.",
        "I have been quite concerned about this event, as a Credit Card is a very sensitive and critical piece of financial instrument for a customer. It carries my personal information like name and date of birth, and in the wrong hands, it can be used to incur financial frauds, causing financial liabilities to me and bringing unwanted stress into my life.",
        "Hence, I request you to kindly take appropriate steps to prevent any misuse of this credit card, either by hot-listing or cancelling the card. Further, I shall also request you to issue a new credit card without any renewal charges, as I believe the current problem has been caused by the negligence of the Bank.",
        "Yours Sincerely,",
        "Kevin Smith"
